US.title: US WAREHOUSE SERVICE FEE (Products Existed or Sourced in CJ US Warehouse)
US.desc: We charge only product fee and shipping cost when you are dropshipping products directly from our US warehouse. The price already mentioned on app.cjdropshipping.com
US.mainTitle: US WAREHOUSE SERVICE FEE (Products NOT Existed in Our US Warehouse)
US.emphasis: = PROCESSING FEE + SHIPPING FEE + WAREHOUSE FEE
US.rightTitleDesc: Shipping Cost=Shipping from China to US + US Domestic
US.rightSecondContent:
Click Your name > Tool > Shipping Calculation

Select shipping method by USPS+ and input the order weight, then the shipping cost will show up.

bottomList1.conditions: The first 30 days for new customers
After the first 30 days for new customers
Low inventory turnover rate
Daily processing on the SKU is over 100 orders and monthly turn over rate is above 50%

bottomList2.conditions: Stocktaking Fee: Any inventory that needs stock-taking, i.e. containers that includes multiple SKU
Packaging material and supplies: Packaging materials, materials that cost more than $0.2 will be charged additionally
Packaging Fee: Putting products into packaging materials
Labeling Fee: Putting labels for products
